import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import App from './App'
import { BrowserRouter } from 'react-router-dom'
import './index.css'

const rootBox=document.getElementById('root')
const root=ReactDOM.createRoot(rootBox)
root.render(
<BrowserRouter>
<App/>
</BrowserRouter>

)
